      "text": [
        " - «إِذَا أَدْرَكَ اَلرَّجُلُ اَلتَّكْبِيرَةَ وَ اَلتَّكْبِيرَتَيْنِ مِنَ اَلصَّلاَةِ عَلَى اَلْمَيِّتِ فَلْيَقْضِ مَا بَقِيَ مُتَتَابِعاً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.471 - Al-Halabi narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) that He said:\n\"If a person catches one or two takbirs of the funeral prayer over the deceased, they should complete the remaining takbirs consecutively.\""
        ]
